  "texts": [
    "The Hard catalogue is a subsample of the 3B catalogue.Most of the source information is calculated in multiple bands and thus a band suffix is printed in the column names.",
    "Tables D.2 and D.3 provide a dictionary for the energy band definitions in the 1B and 3B catalogues, respectively.",
    "A few columns are from the PSF-fitting of source detection using the ermldet task, e.g., DET_LIKE, ML_RATE, ML_CTS, ML_FLUX, EXT, and EXT_LIKE.",
    "In the 3B detection, the band index 1, 2, and 3 indicate 0.2-0.6, 0.6-2.3, and 2.3-5 keV, and band 0 indicates all-band summary values.",
    "In the 1B detection, only band 1 (0.2-2.3 keV) is involved, and the all-band summary value (band 0) is identical to that of band 1."
  ],
